  "body": "<!-- Have you done the following? -->\r\n<!--   * read the Code of Conduct? By filing an Issue, you are expected to -->  \r\n<!--     comply with it, including treating everyone with respect: -->\r\n<!--     https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/master/CODE-OF-CONDUCT.md -->\r\n<!--   * Reproduced the issue in the latest version of the software -->\r\n<!--   * Read the debugging wiki: https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/wiki/debugging -->\r\n<!--   * Duplicate Issue check:  https://github.com/search?q=+is%3Aissue+repo%3Ahyperledger/Besu -->\r\n<!-- Note:  Not all sections will apply to all issue types. -->\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nThere is a cast exception when pruning is enabled. \r\n\r\n```\r\nclass org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.bonsai.BonsaiWorldStateArchive cannot be cast to class org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.worldstate.DefaultWorldStateArchive (org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.bonsai.BonsaiWorldStateArchive and org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.worldstate.DefaultWorldStateArchive are in unnamed module of loader 'app')\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe error seems to be related to this line https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/5241747ba4a62e08953b9584ae03732196b69795/besu/src/main/java/org/hyperledger/besu/controller/BesuControllerBuilder.java#L259\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Besu start to sync without crashing \r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n1. Run besu with this otions \r\n```\r\n--logging=\"INFO\" --network=goerli --data-path=/goerli-bonsai --fast-sync-min-peers=2 --sync-mode=FAST --discovery-enabled=true --pruning-enabled=true --Xdata-storage-format=BONSAI\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n### Versions (Add all that apply)\r\n* Software version: Master (5241747ba4a62e08953b9584ae03732196b69795)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
